# Four corner uprights expose the glow center from all cardinal angles.

# --- 4 CORNER UPRIGHTS (sy=0+1) ---
S 0 0 0  0 0 0  Metal
S 0 0 0  0 1 0  Metal
S 0 0 0  2 0 0  Metal
S 0 0 0  2 1 0  Metal
S 0 0 0  0 0 2  Metal
S 0 0 0  0 1 2  Metal
S 0 0 0  2 0 2  Metal
S 0 0 0  2 1 2  Metal

# --- TOP HOOK (sy=2, center) ---
S 0 0 0  1 2 1  Metal

# --- GLOW INTERIOR ---
S 0 0 0  1 1 1  glow
